hive.org/web/20050403170537/http://cliki.tunes.org/Max">Max</a> &nbsp; <a class="internal" href="https://web.archive.org/web/20050403170537/http://cliki.tunes.org/Memory">Memory</a> &nbsp; <a class="internal" href="https://web.archive.org/web/20050403170537/http://cliki.tunes.org/Meta-Object%20Protocol">Meta-Object Protocol</a> &nbsp; <a class="internal" href="https://web.archive.org/web/20050403170537/http://cliki.tunes.org/Meta-System%20Transition">Meta-System Transition</a> &nbsp; <a class="internal" href="https://web.archive.org/web/20050403170537/http://cliki.tunes.org/MetaML">MetaML</a> &nbsp; <a class="internal" href="https://web.archive.org/web/20050403170537/http://cliki.tunes.org/Methods%20of%20Reflection">Methods of Reflection</a> &nbsp; <a class="internal" href="https://web.archive.org/web/20050403170537/http://cliki.tunes.org/PoLITe%20project">PoLITe project</a> &nbsp; <a class="internal" href="https://web.archive.org/web/20050403170537/http://cliki.tunes.org/Reflection">Reflection</a> &nbsp; <a class="internal" href="https://web.archive.org/web/20050403170537/http://cliki.tunes.org/Smalltalk">Smalltalk</a> &nbsp; <a class="internal" href="https://web.archive.org/web/20050403170537/http://cliki.tunes.org/Sprint">Sprint</a> &nbsp; <a class="internal" href="https://web.archive.org/web/20050403170537/http://cliki.tunes.org/TOM">TOM</a> &nbsp; <a class="internal" href="https://web.archive.org/web/20050403170537/http://cliki.tunes.org/Tube">Tube</a> &nbsp; <a class="internal" href="https://web.archive.org/web/20050403170537/http://cliki.tunes.org/zzz">zzz</a> &nbsp; </div><div id="footer"><form action="https://web.archive.org/web/20050403170537/http://cliki.tunes.org/admin/search"><a class="internal" href="https://web.archive.org/web/20050403170537/http://cliki.tunes.org/edit/Metaprogramming">Edit page</a> | <a class="internal" href="https://web.archive.org/web/20050403170537/http://cliki.tunes.org/Metaprogramming?source">View source</a> | Revisions: <b titl